name: Newsrebound
overview:
Newsrebound is a free, independent, and non-commercial news aggregator portal! It riverberates all news across the world to the general public from major news sources.

Newsrebound is a project with primary objective to freely converge major news headlines in one place, and freely link people to the reliable news providers. The project is a non-commercial and independent one which is opened for any volunteers who are interested to keep people informed by linking them to trusted news providers.

  • To rebound news and blogs to newsrebound, You must abide with the fact that Newsrebound is a free,  independent, and non-commercial news headlines provider. Any rebounded news with or without images MUST completely provide credits and links to the news or blogs’ owners.

Currently, Newsrebound is run alone by the creator who is also the editor of the site. Also, the number of the site’s visitors is becoming increasing everyday; a great challenge that may prompt the creator to seek external funding and support to accommodate a community of large number of visitors.
